                type="document" xml:id="d260">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No official record of this informal meeting has been found. The meeting is
                    mentioned in <persName corresp="#p_AHH1">Arnold</persName>, p. 462, in <persName
                        corresp="#p_LWD1">Leahy</persName>, p. 200, and in <persName
                        corresp="#p_BSA1">Alan-brooke</persName>, p. 52, but there are no
                    indications that matters of business were discussed. The meeting took place in
                    the villa occupied by the British Chiefs of Staff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
